---
import { categories } from "../../../data/shadow-studio/gallery";
import GalleryFilter from "./GalleryFilter.astro";
---

<header
  class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center mb-10 md:mb-24"
>
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full select-none pointer-events-none overflow-hidden flex justify-center items-center opacity-10 z-0"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <span
      class="text-[12rem] md:text-[20rem] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-primary leading-none whitespace-nowrap animate-pulse-slow"
    >
      SHADOW
    </span>
  </div>

  <div
    class="animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-4 transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
  >
    <span
      class="inline-block py-1 px-4 border border-aux-secondary/20 rounded-full bg-primarybg/50 backdrop-blur-sm text-aux-secondary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 shadow-[0_0_15px_-5px_rgba(227,160,70,0.3)]"
    >
      Colección Exclusiva
    </span>
  </div>

  <h2
    class="animate-on-scroll opacity-0 scale-95 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out delay-100 md:mb-6"
  >
    <span
      class="block text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-widest mb-1"
    >
      EL ARTE DE
    </span>
    <span
      class="block text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.85]"
    >
      <span
        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary via-primary to-[#4a0a22] filter drop-shadow-2xl"
      >
        ETERNIZAR
      </span>
    </span>
  </h2>

  <p
    class="animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-4 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out delay-200 mt-2 text-gray-400 font-light text-base md:text-xl max-w-xl leading-relaxed mx-auto"
  >
    Cada pieza es un diálogo entre la piel y la aguja. Explora nuestra selección
    curada de obras maestras recientes.
  </p>

  <div
    class="animate-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out delay-300 mt-12"
  >
    <GalleryFilter categories={categories} />
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  @keyframes pulseSlow {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: scale(1);
      opacity: 0.1;
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      opacity: 0.15;
    }
  }

  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulseSlow 12s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
